Subject: [PATCH 1/9] arm: imx7d: add support for Compulab cl-som-imx7

Add initial support for Compulab cl-som-imx7 SoM.
The initial support includes:
 - MMC
 - eMMC
 - SPI flash
 - I2C
 - FEC
 - USB
 - Serial console

